condition.narrative: Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section I.B.5 (a).The Borrower shall ensure that the NBG adopts the Payment Systems Manual no laterthan thirty (30) days after the Signature Date, in a manner acceptable to the Bank.

Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section I.E.1 and I.E.2. The Borrower shall, and shall cause EG and the NBG to, ensure that the Projectis carried out in accordance with the Environmental and Social Standards, and implemented in accordance with the Environmental andSocial Commitment Plan (“ESCP”), all in a manner acceptable to the Bank.

Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section IV. The Borrower shall ensure that EG, not later than ninety (90) days after the EffectiveDate, has introduced a module within its existing accounting system for Project accounting and reporting, in a manner satisfactoryto the Bank.
